<AbstractNarration>PI proposes to continue his study of Alexandrov spaces and convergence and collapsing of Riemannian manifolds with lower curvature bounds.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Alexandrov geometry is a powerful technique in modern geometry.&lt;br/&gt;It makes it possible to attack important conjectures via axiomatic methods similar to those of classical Euclidean geometry. At the same time it gives a more satisfactory form for many geometric results.&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
